	â€¢	When cumulative margin calls exceed B â†’ fund defaults, broker unwinds.
	â€¢	Default probability = chance margin losses exceed buffer within MPR (Margin Period of Risk).
	â€¢	Creates a structural (not reduced-form) model: default arises from the dynamics of the portfolioâ€™s margin losses.

